title: 77 Sunset Strip - Season 2 incomplete (updated torrent)
description:
From Wikipedia:
77 Sunset Strip is an hour-length American television private detective series created by Roy Huggins and starring Efrem Zimbalist Jr., Roger Smith, and Edd Byrnes. The show was the subject of an ownership battle between Roy Huggins and Warner Brothers, which was the proximate cause of Huggins' departure from the studio. The series was based on novels and short stories written by Huggins prior to his arrival at Warner, but, as a matter of legal record, derived from a brief Caribbean theatrical release of its pilot, Girl on the Run. The show ran for six seasons from 1958 to 1964.

This torrent contains 13 of the 36 episodes from season 2. Eight of these videos are not 100% downloaded, as indicated on their file labels. However, there are almost no problems viewing them.

My previous torrent was missing episode 235 (The Silent Caper).
